Package: ddnsd
Architecture: any
Depends:
 jq, curl, coreutils (>= 8), nano, systemd,
Description: Dynamic DNS client for updating DNS records
 ddnsd is a dynamic DNS client that updates DNS records based on the current
 public IP address of the system. It supports multiple DNS providers and can
 be configured to run as a systemd service.
 .
 It uses an external IP lookup service to determine the current public IP
 address and updates the DNS records accordingly.
